---
/**
 * Disclaimer — AZ Law Now
 */

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="AZ Law Now legal disclaimer. Important information about the content on this website and attorney advertising."
  canonical="/disclaimer/"
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <h1 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--neutral-500); margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <h2>Attorney Advertising</h2>
      <p>
        This website is attorney advertising. The information on this site is for general informational purposes and doesn't constitute legal advice. Don't act on information from this website without consulting a licensed attorney about your specific situation.
      </p>

      <h2>No Attorney-Client Relationship</h2>
      <p>
        No attorney-client relationship is formed by your use of this website, submission of a contact form, or communication through any channel until both parties execute a written representation agreement. All prospective case information is treated as confidential, but privilege doesn't attach until the relationship is formalized.
      </p>

      <h2>Case Results</h2>
      <p>
        Case results shown on this website aren't a guarantee of future performance. Every case is unique. The outcome of your case depends on its specific facts, applicable law, and the actions of all parties involved. Prior results don't predict or guarantee a similar outcome in any future case.
      </p>

      <h2>Jurisdiction</h2>
      <p>
        AZ Law Now is licensed to practice law in the State of Arizona. Information on this website relates to Arizona law unless otherwise stated. If your legal matter involves a different state, you should consult an attorney licensed in that jurisdiction.
      </p>

      <h2>Testimonials and Reviews</h2>
      <p>
        Client testimonials and reviews on this website reflect the individual experiences of those clients. They don't guarantee that your experience or outcome will be the same. Each client's situation is different, and results depend on the specific circumstances of the case.
      </p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        Links to external websites are provided for convenience. AZ Law Now doesn't endorse, verify, or take responsibility for the content or accuracy of external websites.
      </p>

      <h2>Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        We work to keep the information on this website accurate and up to date. We make no warranties or representations about the completeness, reliability, or timeliness of the content. Laws and regulations change frequently. Always verify current legal requirements with a licensed attorney.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this disclaimer? Contact AZ Law Now at <a href="/contact/">our contact page</a> or call <a href="tel:+16026540202">(602) 654-0202</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
